com.jdon.container.access

类 TargetMetaRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jdon.container.access.TargetMetaRequest
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable

    public class TargetMetaRequest
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Every container's user has one UserTargetMetaDef object this object is event DTO when this user enter businerss proxy. it reduce the method's parameters amount; it's scope is event instance for per request of one user ; TargetMetaDef object's scope is for event service for all users;

    banq
